casebody.data:
The State of Ohio, Appellant, v. Calhoun, Appellee.

[Cite as State v. Calhoun, 127 Ohio St.3d 1201, 2010-Ohio-4981.]

*1202(No. 2009-2324 Submitted September 29, 2010 Decided October 19, 2010.)

{¶ 1} The cause is dismissed, sua sponte, as having been improvidently accepted.

Brown, C.J., and Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell, Lanzinger, and Cupp, JJ., concur.
